{"tid":322724,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"你不知道的IU小秘密！《孝利家民宿》打工妹動作慢還喜歡發呆","createTime":"2017-07-15T05:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T16:57:10.000Z","uid":34643,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fadb2a117e958fb73faf2ed49864c6799411e41","tid":322724,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.niusnews.com/upload/imgs/default/2017JulE/0711IU/1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.niusnews.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2Fdefault%2F2017JulE%2F0711IU%2F1.png&h=c1426d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《孝利家民宿》每一集都好治癒，節目步調相當慵懶，而且可以看到李孝利夫婦平凡的生活中，卻有著滿滿的幸福，真的讓人好羨慕！並且還有可愛的IU在裡面當打工妹，齁，這種民宿誰不想去住啊！<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.niusnews.com/upload/imgs/default/2017JulE/0711IU/2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.niusnews.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2Fdefault%2F2017JulE%2F0711IU%2F2.png&h=4fcd6a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前《孝利家民宿》播到第三集啦！在第三集中，我們IU妹妹也似乎對民宿該做得事情越來越清楚、越來越上手了，不過不知道妞妞們有沒有發現，其實IU有幾個不為人知的小秘密噢～讓我們一起來玩IU知多少的遊戲吧～<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1.IU喜歡發呆</div><img src=\"http://imgs.niusnews.com/upload/imgs/default/2017JulE/0711IU/3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.niusnews.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2Fdefault%2F2017JulE%2F0711IU%2F3.gif&h=9728e355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可愛的IU常常不自覺得放空，而且由於節目風格本身就很慵懶，妞編輯總是誤以為自家電視當機了！（笑倒）<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2.不熟練家務</div><img src=\"http://imgs.niusnews.com/upload/imgs/default/2017JulE/0711IU/4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.niusnews.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2Fdefault%2F2017JulE%2F0711IU%2F4.gif&h=9dedea4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU也是第一次擔任民宿的打工妹，很多事情都不熟練，偶爾出差錯的時候還會嚇到客人呢～<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3.上班有時會遲到</div><img src=\"http://imgs.niusnews.com/upload/imgs/default/2017JulE/0711IU/5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.niusnews.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2Fdefault%2F2017JulE%2F0711IU%2F5.gif&h=5147ead2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上班族的苦痛我們IU也懂！因為我們IU也會睡過頭噢～不過還好她老闆孝利夫婦很善良，都能理解的。（不像我們老闆&hellip;）（閉嘴）<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">4.吃飯細嚼慢嚥</div><img src=\"http://imgs.niusnews.com/upload/imgs/default/2017JulE/0711IU/6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.niusnews.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2Fdefault%2F2017JulE%2F0711IU%2F6.gif&h=dfc8ed31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU吃飯超、級、慢！每口都細嚼慢嚥，甚至有些時候還邊洗碗邊咬，整個很有趣。 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">5.喜歡睡午覺</div><img src=\"http://imgs.niusnews.com/upload/imgs/default/2017JulE/0711IU/7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.niusnews.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2Fdefault%2F2017JulE%2F0711IU%2F7.gif&h=1362edaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看IU睡覺莫名的療癒耶～（盯著）怎麼睡相這麼乖巧啊？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">6.動作慢吞吞</div><img src=\"http://imgs.niusnews.com/upload/imgs/default/2017JulE/0711IU/8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.niusnews.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2Fdefault%2F2017JulE%2F0711IU%2F8.gif&h=ca42ff03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU作為打工妹，有一個大大的缺點就是動作很慢，不過，雖然IU動作慢慢的，但會堅持把事情做到最好，這點很值得大家學習噢！<br />\n<br />\n[url][/url]<br />\n看完以上，妞編輯深深覺得，我們IU根本是小貓咪吧！動作都有點慵慵懶懶的，整個超級萌！那以上IU的小秘密粉絲們都知道嗎？如果還想知道更多的IU小秘密，那就千萬不要錯過超療癒節目《孝利家民宿》噢！"},{"pid":"b6f7fdd91a470180a3625ebd42d082ee289bccd9","tid":322724,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QZDQuXFDE4U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQZDQuXFDE4U&d=PdSOQmTyTqY3Gw2N2DLm1ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=260e7f9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QZDQuXFDE4U</a>"},{"pid":"31b672db3c1bfa52a8f3800cf47112cd7b413768","tid":322724,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T05:27:07.000Z","msg":"世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/